-02-Antheya-III-10.jpg&h=b525c887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我中意呢隻多d，入少少，寫意d。<br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通 中式船。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media1.88db.com.hk/DB88UploadFiles/2013/09/25/DCAB7408-9136-4B93-8534-7368E476F586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.88db.com.hk%2FDB88UploadFiles%2F2013%2F09%2F25%2FDCAB7408-9136-4B93-8534-7368E476F586.jpg&h=cce2e407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今晚 , 7點尖沙咀碼頭集合 <br />\n男仔：$1500 位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通女仔：屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$1500去船河的人吧。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"b63112cc1cce8940bcca5b4ae5b5c21df5c2d016","tid":1826031,"uid":202348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:07:42.000Z","msg":"小花咁早起身"},{"pid":"4509e18d39e667f809391ea5e23166075b908580","tid":1826031,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:10:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8fe2e42340c6e0cc03f7607107ab9e59dabe9c2","tid":1826031,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b63112cc1cce8940bcca5b4ae5b5c21df5c2d016","tid":1826031,"uid":202348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:07:42.000Z","msg":"小花咁早起身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:23:24.000Z","msg":"因為我未能訓"},{"pid":"064bcd901c3ff9729c731b9638cd4891d09ef0cf","tid":1826031,"uid":203961,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:28:16.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會無咩人想知？<br />\n<br />\n幫手推行動post 唔該"},{"pid":"3a18344be9161d4f4b7772bd92a80a91fa29be30","tid":1826031,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"064bcd901c3ff9729c731b9638cd4891d09ef0cf","tid":1826031,"uid":203961,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:28:16.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會無咩人想知？<br />\n<br />\n幫手推行動post 唔該"},"cit